headline: Crypto's winning week capped by David Sacks's ascension to Trump White House
summary: The appointment of David Sacks as Donald Trump’s new 'AI and crypto czar' capped a week of wins for the crypto world, putting an advocate for looser regulation of digital assets inside the White House.

headline: The next S&P 500 shake-up could usher in Coinbase, Block, or these other stocks
summary: The S 500 index committee makes quarterly changes, with Robinhood and Vertiv among other companies that meet the criteria. But choosing new entrants is “more art than science.”
